    12→ *
    13→ * This is a CRITICAL service for MMS v2.1:
    14→ * - Accurate mileage projections are essential for PM scheduling
    15→ * - Fleet-wide averages can cause 60,000+ km projection errors over 12 years
    16→ * - Route-specific profiles provide the highest accuracy
    17→ *
    18→ * @see src/services/route-utilization.ts
